  m_text: "<b>Bait</b> \u2014 Select a Pok\xE9mon in the shop, then click the Bait
    button to lock that slot. A baited slot is marked and will not be replaced when
    you reroll \u2014 useful when you see a Pok\xE9mon you want but can't afford
    yet.\n\n<b>Release</b> \u2014 Select a Pok\xE9mon on your battle row or bench,
    then press the Release button. The Pok\xE9mon is gone immediately \u2014 no refund
    is given, so only release when you're sure you no longer need it."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
