  m_text: "Your goal is to earn <b>8 Gym Badges</b> by defeating Gym Leaders.\n\nEach
    badge you collect unlocks a harder opponent and expands the tier of Pok\xE9mon
    available in the shop.\n\nOnce all 8 badges are yours, you face the <b>Elite
    Four</b>. Each Elite Four member is followed by a shop break so you can adjust
    your team.\n\nDefeat all four and you earn the right to challenge the <b>Champion</b>.
    Defeat the Champion to complete your run and enter the Hall of Fame."
